name: Cactus Jactus protects the world's greatest secret from the prying eyes of the common man
name_original: Cactus Jactus protects the world's greatest secret from the prying eyes of the common man
description:
Made as part of the Cactus Game Jam.

We're in trouble Jactus. Humans are getting close to finding out that cacti aren't the friendly green pricks they appear in movies. They're actually inter-dimensional squatters enjoying the cushy life here on earth. It's up to you to keep the cactus' mutations under control so those idiots out there are none the wiser. We're sending you to the world's most popular tourist attraction, the cactus from that one episode of Jackass. 

Keep it pruned as long as you can, cactus kind everywhere is relying on you!

Cactus Jactus!
